title: Elvis Presley 6-10-72
description:
Here is a very nice Elvis gem. Check my account for more classic bootlegs.

Please enjoy, share with friends and please seed :)


Elvis At The Garden
10 June 1972
Madison Square Garden
Afternoon & Evening Shows

An excellent DVD from Unicorn with digitally remastered footage of the original 8mm films taken by fans
during Elvis Presley's two shows at Madison Square Garden on 10 June 1972. Although are not complete they give an excellent idea of how dynamic Elvis was on stage in the early 70s.
